data.description: Great opportunity to own a detached 3 bedroom home in Jamaica NY. On the main level there is a large living room, full bathroom, kitchen and 1 bedroom. Walk up to the second level to find 2 additional bedrooms. There is a large backyard with private parking and large driveway that fits multiple cars. Location is everything with this home. Right off the Van Wyck. Bus Q20A, Q31, Q54, Q56, Q60. The E, F, FX, J trains are nearby as well. Home needs TLC. Fixer Upper. As-Is, Estate Sale, Subject To Court Approval.
